FOR SALE: $220,000 on Lake George, Wales

Restored antique cape and barn with Lake George waterfront property.Unique home recently restored and updated while remaining true to it's 1800's roots. This is one of the original waterfront properties.

Antique barn/ carriage shed was formerly used as an antiques/gift shop. Second floor of the barn is the ideal studio and treasured get-away space.

Property includes a private, fenced in waterfront lot with shed and deck area on Lake George, Wales.

Step back in time and enjoy the simple life. A perfect vacation home or year round residence that brings one back to the ‘good old days’.

Living room with built in cabinets, recently restored fireplace and mouldings along with many original doors lovingly restored.

Sunny ‘old style’ kitchen with room for several chefs.

Charmingly remodeled kitchen is in the former 1916 schoolhouse section with modern appliances designed to blend into the country kitchen.
